title: Taylor loses big time at the EMAs
text:
Taylor Swift loses big time at the EMAs AAP Taylor Swift loses big time at the EMAs AAP Taylor Swift loses big time at the EMAs. 
IT WASN’T Taylor Swift’s night at the 2016 MTV Europe Music Awards in Milan, winning only one out of the nine awards she was nominated for. 
Swift took home Best Song for hit “Bad Blood” featuring hip hop artist Kendrick Lamar. 
The “Shake It Off” singer wasn’t able to accept her award in person as she’s currently on tour in Atlanta. 
Swift was also nominated for Best Collaboration, Best Look, Biggest Fan, Best Live Act, Best Pop, Best Female and Best Video. Instead, 2015 belonged to Justin Bieber who won four of the six awards he was nominated for. 
Here is the full list of winners for this year’s EMAs: 
BEST SONG
